N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 663.8 - Appeals and review

State Regulations

An appeal from, or an application for review of, a
decision, determination or order under this Part may be made to the freshwater
wetlands appeals board or to a court of competent jurisdiction in accordance
with the provisions of title 11 of the act. Notes
